<br>
They do certainly add a new depth of community to the forums, but at the same time add a &quot;ok, which forum is which again?&quot; problem.<br>
<br>
Now that you're planning to have newbie, high end, and general discussions all in one forum, we seriously need more moderation to keep atitudes in check.  Even if the question has been asked 10000 times before, there's no need to slam the asker.  Just point them to the Guide we'd have by then, lock the thread, and delete it in a day or two.<br>
